# ForgeNX App Store

Application store and app definitions for ForgeNX, including install manifests, containers and service integrations.

## Planned Scope

### App Packaging
- Application manifests
- Container definitions
- Service templates
- Dependency declarations

### App Categories
- Node applications
- Mining applications
- Infrastructure services
- Utilities and tooling

### App Lifecycle
- Install
- Update
- Backup
- Remove
- Health monitoring

## Goals
ForgeNX App Store aims to provide a simple, reproducible framework for deploying and managing applications on ForgeNX systems.

## Future Structure
```text
apps/
manifests/
templates/
catalog/
scripts/
```

## Status
Initial repository scaffold.
